						<summary>

						<p>On a pillar in the <hi rend="italic">kalyānamaṇḍapa</hi> in the Viṭṭhalēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>13th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This incomplete record is dated in the Cyclic year Āngīrasa, Chaitra, ba. 1, Wednesday. The record can be assigned to 13th century A.D. on palaeographical grounds.</p>						

						<p>It mentions a tax collector <hi rend="italic">(sunkādhikāri)</hi> Pōnkala Mallayya Gōvinda Peggaḍa.</p>						

